Revision history for Perinci-Sub-Gen

0.03    2015-09-04 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.02     2014-08-04 (SHARYANTO)

         - Make 'name' argument optional (it's only required if we do install).


0.01     2012-08-10 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release. Split to avoid circular dependency problem of Perinci
           -> Setup::Symlink -> Perinci::Sub::Gen::Undoable -> Perinci::Sub::Gen
           (in Perinci-Sub-Gen-AccessTable -> Perinci::CmdLine ->
           Perinci::Access (in Perinci)). Boy, dependency is hard. :)
